These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
House: gothic-revival, tower, victorian, art-deco
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, davidoff, old-henry, bluemaster
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the victorian house##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
3. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
5. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| House   | gothic-revival | tower | art-deco | victorian |
| Cigar        | siglo | davidoff   | bluemaster | old-henry    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
House: farmhouse, cottage, colonial, modern
4 different games are played: poker, canasta, scrabble, domino
1. the cottage house is on the left of the modern house##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing poker is the farmhouse house##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
6. the person playing poker is the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| House   | colonial | farmhouse  | cottage  | modern |
| Game   | domino    | poker | scrabble | canasta    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, march, may
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, yellow, aquamarine, white
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
2. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
4. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
5. the person who likes ebony is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Birthday          | may | march | february    | june      |
| Color   | aquamarine        | white     | ebony | yellow |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, rowing, cricket, weightlifting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, sports, documentary, animation
1. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching animation movies##2
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | skiing | rowing | cricket |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary       | comedy   | sports    | animation  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, ferret, turtle, goat
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, bike, taxi, boat
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the bike is the owner of the goat##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
6. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Pet   | ferret  | rat    | turtle   | goat       |
| Transport   | tram | boat | taxi | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, weightlifting, sailing, snowboarding
4 different games are played: scrabble, go, monopoly, billiard
1. the person playing go is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person playing go##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Sport   | sailing      | weightlifting | snowboarding | swimming |
| Game   | billiard | go     | scrabble  | monopoly  |

