.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, milk, coffee
House: tower, modern, townhouse, ranch-style
1. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4
2. the townhouse house is on the left of the tower house##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
4. the ranch-style house is the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the tower house##3
6. the modern house is on the right of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage   | cola | coffee | milk | soy-milk    |
| House     | ranch-style | townhouse  | tower     | modern |

