.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, collecting, magic-tricks, video-games
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, cola, iced-tea
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
6. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
7. the person drinking juice is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person drinking cola##2
8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Hobby   | collecting | dancing      | video-games | magic-tricks |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | iced-tea | juice    | cola            |

