.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, comedy, fantasy, drama
City: hannover, nizza, miami, colone
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is between the person traveling to nizza and the person watching fantasy movies##2
4. the person traveling to hannover is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching fantasy movies is the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | comedy   | family | fantasy |
| City    | colone     | nizza | hannover     | miami  |

