.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, russian, french, german
There 4 different types of food: peas, cherry, pineapple, mango
1. the australian is the person eating mango##1
2. the person eating peas is on the right of the australian##1
3. the person eating mango is between the person eating peas and the french##2
4. the australian is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3
6. the russian is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Nationality      | russian       | french   | australian | german |
| Food   | pineapple | cherry | mango        | peas    |

