.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, architect, designer, project-manager
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, house, rock, hip-hop
1. the fan of pop is in an even position##4
2. the fan of rock is on the right of the social-worker##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the designer##1
5. the architect is on the left or right of the designer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Job   | social-worker   | project-manager   | architect      | designer      |
| Music-Genre      | house | rock | hip-hop | pop |

