2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
3. the lawyer is in an even position##4
4. the nurse is on the far right##1
5. the chef is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is reading##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Job          | manager | lawyer  | chef  | nurse |
| Hobby   | drawing  | reading | puzzles | woodworking   |

