2. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
6. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3

.:: Answer ::.
