.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, soy-milk, cola
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, argentine, american, australian
1. the person drinking iced-tea is between the egyptian and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the australian##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the australian is in an odd position##4
6. the american is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | cola | mirinda         | iced-tea   | soy-milk |
| Nationality   | american    | argentine | australian | egyptian   |

