2. the entrepreneur is the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the pilot is the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
5. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up | mirinda | fanta    | sprite |
| Job   | firefighter   | entrepreneur  | writer | pilot     |

