.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, december, july
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, almond-milk, milk
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking juice is the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
5. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking almond-milk##2
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday         | july   | december | august | april    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | juice  | milk     | water |

