.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, spy, drama, disaster
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, folk, punk, gospel
1. the fan of folk is on the far left##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
6. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
7. the fan of r&b is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | western    | drama       | spy |
| Music-Genre       | folk  | punk | gospel | r&b  |

