.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, may, april
City: hamburg, boston, venice, miami
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Birthday   | february | may | september  | april |
| City     | hamburg      | venice       | boston | miami     |

