.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, rose, sunflower, poppy
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, iced-tea, sprite
1. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
3. the person drinking fanta is between the person who growsiris and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Flower         | iris | sunflower   | poppy | rose |
| Beverage   | sprite          | fanta | 7up         | iced-tea  |

 